    height="2048"
    alt="Portrait of Poppy outside a library. A smiling young woman with long red hair wears a dark green cardigan, cream blouse and burgundy patterned skirt. She carries a large brown leather satchel filled with books. A sign beside her reads: The Library. All knowledge has been read. Ask wisely."
